27th of October 1981

00:22.400 --> 00:30.400
Happy Diwali, Mother.

00:36.920 --> 00:38.040
He is very happy.

00:41.720 --> 00:44.720
Datta, what's happening to you?

00:45.320 --> 00:46.640
Very happy.

00:47.400 --> 00:48.400
All the joy.

00:51.200 --> 00:52.920
All are catching here, are they?

00:57.760 --> 00:59.640
Left Vishuddhi?

