Gayle, Gayle is not there and we have to wait for Gavin also.

01:14.440 --> 01:15.720
Gayle has not come as yet?

01:15.880 --> 01:17.440
She is here. She's just gone out.

01:17.720 --> 01:18.720
All right, she is here.

01:18.920 --> 01:20.960
So, she must have told Warwick Road people.

01:21.280 --> 01:23.800
Mother, Jeremy is working, Mother.

01:23.960 --> 01:26.360
And he is in Cambridge.

01:26.640 --> 01:27.640
Who is?

01:27.840 --> 01:29.080
Jeremy is working.

01:29.280 --> 01:30.320
Working where?

01:30.640 --> 01:32.600
He's at work tonight.

01:34.680 --> 01:35.600
All right.

01:36.080 --> 01:39.080
He lives in Cambridge. So then Chhaya ...

01:39.200 --> 01:42.040
Come along. Hello. How is Magda?

01:42.560 --> 01:43.440
She’s come?

01:43.720 --> 01:44.220
Coming, yes.

01:44.320 --> 01:45.720
All right, good, good.

01:45.960 --> 01:48.200
May God bless you. You are all looking so nice.

01:48.320 --> 01:49.880
Thank You, Mother.

01:50.200 --> 01:52.960
Both of you, really looking very nice.

01:55.400 --> 01:56.960
Not very cold outside, is it?

01:57.440 --> 01:58.440
No.

01:58.800 --> 02:00.960
