02:01.080 --> 02:02.280
Yes, exactly, isn't it?

02:02.840 --> 02:04.120
It was very cold, was that?

02:04.720 --> 02:06.040
Yes, it was.

02:07.560 --> 02:10.040
Actually, when we were coming by plane only, they announced

02:10.120 --> 02:11.320
it's three degrees.

02:11.680 --> 02:15.120
And then I've seen the temperature suddenly rose after that.

02:24.920 --> 02:26.640
Now you have to start walking.

02:27.400 --> 02:28.400
All right?

02:28.960 --> 02:29.960
Come along.

02:46.960 --> 02:48.400
This one is also very happy.

02:50.920 --> 02:51.800
All right?

02:57.640 --> 02:59.640
Very happy.

03:00.960 --> 03:02.120
Linda, take him back.

03:02.920 --> 03:04.560
As a... Where has she gone?

03:04.720 --> 03:05.600
She's not here.

03:05.720 --> 03:07.640
All right, then let her come. Let her come then.

03:07.920 --> 03:09.640
So how are you, all of you?

03:09.960 --> 03:11.200
Happy, Magda?

03:11.960 --> 03:14.400
Very happy to be here, Mother.

03:16.720 --> 03:18.120
America was difficult.

03:18.560 --> 03:20.960
Not so simple, I knew that.

03:22.240 --> 03:23.440
But we've done it, I mean

03:23.800 --> 03:25.960
we've got centers everywhere now, in New York,

03:26.600 --> 03:27.920
we've got centers in,

03:29.320 --> 03:30.800
what's that place, is

03:31.960 --> 03:32.960
Santa Cruz,

03:33.160 --> 03:36.560
then one, maybe in Santa Monica we might get one

03:37.080 --> 03:39.080
and one in Los Angeles,

03:40.200 --> 03:41.760
one in,

03:47.120 --> 03:48.280
maybe Vancouver,

03:48.600 --> 03:51.640
I don't know, if we are about to have it, one there.

03:53.720 --> 03:54.720
Like that.

03:59.120 --> 04:01.800
The only place we didn't go was San Francisco.

04:05.760 --> 04:06.960
What a nice sari!

04:07.680 --> 04:08.680
Looking so nice.

04:11.040 --> 04:14.360
This is the, all the spring colours are there in the sari.

04:17.280 --> 04:19.960
You see, what you should do is to stitch it up for her

04:20.120 --> 04:23.160
so that it is easier for her to wear like a lehenga.

04:23.720 --> 04:25.960
And you will also have a sari, will you?

04:26.160 --> 04:27.760
You want to have a sari, also?

04:27.960 --> 04:29.720
Ha, Nicki?

04:29.960 --> 04:32.120
I'll get you one small sari, all right?

04:33.400 --> 04:35.640
And then you can wear it like this, like her.

04:37.640 --> 04:38.640
No?

04:38.920 --> 04:40.040
You feel shy?

04:43.720 --> 04:44.800
Did she go to Maria?

04:45.440 --> 04:46.640
Yes, she's happy.

04:46.840 --> 04:48.200
Is she quite happy with Maria?

04:48.320 --> 04:48.960
Yes.

04:55.960 --> 04:57.960
Maria has a problem, a little bit.

05:01.680 --> 05:04.840
What about Pat and all these people? Are they not back from work?

05:05.560 --> 05:06.320
Grace is coming.

05:06.600 --> 05:07.280
Grace?

05:07.400 --> 05:08.240
Grace will be coming here.

05:08.320 --> 05:09.800
Coming.

05:17.440 --> 05:20.440
And Houston of course, Houston was such a big success.

05:21.080 --> 05:23.840
For the first meeting there were forty-five people.

05:24.040 --> 05:25.040
I mean, the repeat.

05:25.680 --> 05:26.840
After My coming so,

05:26.960 --> 05:28.680
already there are forty-five working.

05:30.400 --> 05:32.400
Santa Cruz we had lots of people.

05:33.400 --> 05:34.960
Next time I think we'll do much better,

05:35.120 --> 05:36.920
because I met a man who was very, very

05:37.960 --> 05:40.040
influential person, extremely influential.

05:40.440 --> 05:42.880
He knows all the Congress men, this thing, that thing,

05:42.960 --> 05:44.200
and he's an Indian.

05:44.360 --> 05:45.880
They said if this man does something,

05:46.000 --> 05:47.200
then something will happen.

05:47.720 --> 05:49.160
We went and met him and he was very nice

05:49.360 --> 05:50.920
and he said that, "You should have come

05:51.200 --> 05:52.960
earlier and You should have let me know

05:53.960 --> 05:56.800
of the complete program and then I would have put You

05:56.920 --> 05:59.640
on all the medias and everything, I'll work it out."

06:00.400 --> 06:02.680
He said that, "Next time when You come, give me

06:02.880 --> 06:05.040
at least a month or two months notice and I'll

06:05.440 --> 06:07.920
put You up."  Because to go to these

06:08.560 --> 06:10.240
medias there, it's very difficult

06:10.400 --> 06:12.560
and you have to pay a lot of money just to get into it.

06:14.200 --> 06:15.560
Hello, Pat! How are you?

06:15.800 --> 06:17.880
Hi, Mother. How lovely to see You.

06:18.840 --> 06:19.840
What about David?

06:19.960 --> 06:21.560
Is he not coming?

06:21.720 --> 06:24.680
I think, I don't know. David, he stays here?

06:25.760 --> 06:26.880
Yes, Mother.

06:28.640 --> 06:29.960
Are you, are you recording?

06:32.360 --> 06:33.960
Keep it for a while, then do it.

06:36.600 --> 06:38.560
So anybody who is trying to come?

06:40.720 --> 06:41.760
Are there any plans?

06:44.880 --> 06:45.880
In England?

06:49.600 --> 06:50.600
Not yet known.

06:52.040 --> 06:54.960
Annie from France will come in India.

06:55.120 --> 06:58.240
France people are different, but from England, those who are coming.

07:00.160 --> 07:02.120
What do you think, Nick? Why don't you come?

07:03.600 --> 07:04.240
If I can go, yes.

07:04.560 --> 07:05.880
Nick, you should, I think.

07:06.040 --> 07:07.320
It will be a good idea.

07:08.800 --> 07:10.200
Will be good idea for you.

07:10.760 --> 07:12.680
What about you, Cathy? All right.

07:16.600 --> 07:17.840
Marcus, what do you think?

07:18.160 --> 07:19.240
I've been for certain years.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.200
You should try,

07:20.600 --> 07:21.960
it would be a good idea.

07:23.160 --> 07:24.560
All left-sided people.

07:27.080 --> 07:28.680
It's a good idea.

07:29.600 --> 07:32.400
What do you think about? Felicity?

07:33.960 --> 07:35.120
Where is she?

07:37.560 --> 07:38.880
I'd like to be there.

07:38.960 --> 07:40.280
You have no money?

07:41.080 --> 07:43.400
Well, I'm working. You see, I

07:43.600 --> 07:45.880
it's just when I start teaching again.

07:46.400 --> 07:47.960
So, you won't be able to take leave?

07:48.160 --> 07:49.800
Maybe for Australia, Mother, but ...

07:51.120 --> 07:53.440
Australia but not India.

07:53.800 --> 07:55.080
You can go to Australia?

07:55.200 --> 07:58.120
Yes, that might be my future holiday.

08:00.960 --> 08:04.040
It's difficult taking time off work, because we get holidays.

08:04.200 --> 08:06.720
If you are going to Australia will be no change to you.

08:08.400 --> 08:10.960
I mean, India is the place where one should go.

08:11.400 --> 08:13.680
Australia is another Western country.

08:15.240 --> 08:17.400
I'll ask. I'd like to come, Mother.

08:18.120 --> 08:19.120
Try.

08:20.560 --> 08:23.120
Especially when you go to those villages, it is very

08:25.080 --> 08:26.880
pure land, you know.

08:26.960 --> 08:28.960
People are very pure there.

08:29.200 --> 08:31.320
Isn't it, don't you think so, it helps a lot?

08:32.840 --> 08:36.640
Very simple people and meeting them, you see,

08:36.840 --> 08:38.400
many problems can get solved.

08:41.320 --> 08:42.760
And what about you?

08:43.960 --> 08:45.200
I might go to India.

08:47.240 --> 08:48.240
You try, at least.

09:00.840 --> 09:02.400
I wanted Christine to come.

09:03.160 --> 09:04.560
She requires it very much.

09:07.120 --> 09:08.600
Maybe Kate might come.

09:09.800 --> 09:10.960
Patricia, what about you?

09:11.120 --> 09:12.320
I want to come.

09:13.920 --> 09:16.960
I think you better do it, once again.

09:17.560 --> 09:18.840
Kay is coming as well, Mother.

09:18.960 --> 09:20.280
Kay will be coming, I know.

09:20.880 --> 09:22.160
Mother, I think ...

09:22.920 --> 09:23.920
Who's there?

09:25.120 --> 09:28.320
I think Bernard said he wanted to come and, if he's serious about.

09:28.440 --> 09:29.440
Bernard,

09:29.960 --> 09:32.080
from the hotel said he wanted to go to India.

09:32.320 --> 09:32.820
Is it?

09:32.920 --> 09:33.960
Yes, Mother.

09:34.720 --> 09:35.880
So, get all their names.

09:35.960 --> 09:37.080
What about you?

09:37.960 --> 09:38.840
Me?

09:38.960 --> 09:42.080
I'd love to, Mother, but how am I going to [fund] it though?

09:44.400 --> 09:46.360
Yeah, I mean all those who can manage.

09:47.240 --> 09:48.840
You should experience after all.

09:48.960 --> 09:51.960
You see, the atmosphere and everything...

09:52.240 --> 09:55.560
You know, people are so sensitive there.

09:55.960 --> 09:58.000
Simple people living with simple lives,

09:58.360 --> 10:00.920
not complicated, they don’t think so much,

10:02.280 --> 10:04.920
and their style is very

10:06.560 --> 10:08.960
slow-paced and you have to keep pace with them.

10:09.320 --> 10:12.320
So, you bring down... Neesha has run away.

10:12.920 --> 10:14.200
Last time we were there only for three days,

10:14.400 --> 10:16.720
where they didn't want you to stay there.

10:17.320 --> 10:18.320
We ran out.

10:22.400 --> 10:24.360
Kharus was a good place we went to.

10:25.320 --> 10:26.960
But this time we'll have another route,

10:27.080 --> 10:28.680
some other places we can go to.

