10:37.040 --> 10:39.360
Instead of going by plane, why don't you all go by train

10:39.640 --> 10:42.360
from Bombay to Delhi?

10:46.080 --> 10:48.160
So you can do many other places on the way.

10:54.600 --> 10:58.280
You can go to Baroda, you can go to...

10:58.560 --> 11:00.160
Ahmedabad or something.

11:00.800 --> 11:02.760
It's always good, because you leave your vibrations

11:02.920 --> 11:04.080
in all these places.

11:10.880 --> 11:12.960
You can also go by bus if you want to.

11:13.080 --> 11:14.720
You can have two buses hired.

11:15.720 --> 11:16.720
It will take about...

11:17.200 --> 11:19.400
I think two days to go to Delhi, two days.

11:20.000 --> 11:21.560
Two or three days, at the most.

11:23.360 --> 11:25.400
But, I mean, you'll vibrate the whole place,

11:25.560 --> 11:27.280
you'll go around, it would be good idea.

11:36.880 --> 11:39.840
Good, good, very good, very good, very good.

11:42.960 --> 11:44.160
She knows how far...

11:51.160 --> 11:53.400
She's treating everybody's Agnya and Sahastrara.

11:57.880 --> 11:58.880
No?

11:58.960 --> 11:59.960
Good.

12:00.240 --> 12:01.240
No?

