And she takes out like that also, you know, like this...

12:17.680 --> 12:19.040
That's how they do it.

12:20.440 --> 12:23.560
Even Olympia does that, you must have noticed, like this.

12:29.840 --> 12:31.960
Chhaya has not come, Regis and all these people either.

