14:09.760 --> 14:10.760
How is Pat?

14:10.960 --> 14:11.960
Very well, Mother.

14:12.040 --> 14:13.960
Have you come? All right, come along, sit down.

14:18.900 --> 14:20.200
Linda, you can give him.

14:21.280 --> 14:23.280
I do not want him to to eat all that. Little bit.

